# Contributing

## Style guide

This project uses the [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) formatter.

The code style is verified by Github actions. 

A contributer can verify the style locally by running `yarn check-format`.

In order to auto-format the code, a user can run locally `yarn format`.

## Linting

This project uses the [ESLint](https://eslint.org/) linter.

The linting process is done by Github actions. 

A contributer can lint the code locally by running `yarn lint`.
